Real-Time Currency Converter

This is a real-time currency converter web application that allows users to quickly and accurately convert between different currencies using live exchange rates.

What It Does

Users can select a base currency, enter an amount, and choose the target currency for conversion.
The application fetches live exchange rate data from an external API to provide up-to-date conversion rates.
It displays the converted amount in real-time.

Technologies Used

HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for the frontend.
External API (mention the API name or source) for live exchange rate data.
The project uses the fetch function to retrieve exchange rate data from an external API.
JSON is used to parse and handle the data received from the API.
Ensure that an internet connection is available to fetch the latest exchange rates.
The user interface is designed to be user-friendly and responsive for various devices.




